    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Diaper Diplomacy</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Phil Oliver letter on Jeffrey Goldberg's April 30 column on Jamie Rubin's marriage to Christiane Amanpour notes that caregiving fathers change diapers2</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Caregiving fathers who ''fulfill their responsibilities'' do diapers. The diplomatic distance that served Jamie Rubin so well at Foggy Bottom is no asset at the changing table, where unpleasant realities are not so readily evaded.</p>
        <p>Phil Oliver</p>
        <p>Nashville</p>
      </block>
